          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Run compliant payroll in minutes. Automate PF, ESI, Professional Tax, and TDS. Generate payslips, bank files, and statutory reports — all from one platform.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6 flex-wrap gap-y-4">
            <a href="<%= signup_path %>" class="rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-500 transition hover:shadow-lg">
              Start free trial — no credit card
